<h2 class="bac">Training:</h2>
<p class="bac">
A 10-week program including formal training and assignments in Global Markets product areas. One week of training followed by three 3-week rotations in one of the product areas in fixed income or equity markets and exposure to different functions in sales, trading, origination, and structuring/quantitative analysis. Direct placement in one product area for the entire summer for select areas can be arranged for select groups.
</p>
<br>
<h2 class="bac">Placement</h2>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>Based on current business need in the sales, trading, origination, and structuring/quantitative analysis functions</li>
	<li>Exposure to multiple Global Markets product areas via three 3-week rotations or a direct placement in one product area for the entire summer (available for select areas)</li> 
	<li>Product areas in New York, Charlotte, and Chicago, except Commodities in Houston</li> 
</ul>

